import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
//1.引入自定义组件
import testContainer from "./components/testContainer.vue"
import listContainer from "./components/listContainer.vue"
import HomeContainer from "./components/tabbar/HomeContainer.vue"
import newsListContainer from "./components/news/newsListContainer"
import newInfoContainer from "./components/news/newInfoContainer"
import shopContainer from "./components/tabbar/shopContainer"

Vue.use(Router)
//2.配置访问自定义组件路径
export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/test',component:testContainer},
    {path:'/list',component:listContainer},
    {path:'/home',component:HomeContainer},
    {path:'/home/newslist',component:newsListContainer},
    {path:'/',redirect:'/home'},
    {path:'/home/newsinfo',component:newInfoContainer},
    {path:'/home/shop/:id ',component:shopContainer}
  ]
})
